desc: Top-quality, eco-friendly indoor and outdoor rattan furniture. Ethically and sustainably made by artisans all over the world. For your patio, bedroom, living room, and more. Everything from classic wishbone Y-chairs to boho chic accent pieces, it's a perfect marriage of timeless Scandinavian design and tropical allure.

layout.text: Sustainable, ethical rattan, handmade by artisans all over the world
Transform your home with coastal Scandinavian luxury and a dash of tropical allure
